At least one year of experience in working with relational database systems using structured query language; At least one year of experience in business intelligence and reporting tools such as Power BI, Tableau, SSIS, SSRS, SSAS or Qlik; Familiarity with local and regional workforce and economic development issues, sectoral partnerships, federal and state guidelines governing the American Job Center network, Workforce Innovation and Opportunity Act (WIOA).


